name: The Metamask Dao
description: $MKD is a token created by The Metamask Dao and distributed in the Metamask community. $MKD can be obtained by users who donate with ETH on juicebox and randomly airdropped to Metamask loyal users. We will promote the prosperity of the Metamask community, actively provide valuable opinions to Metamask, and strive to build the world's first wallet for Metamask.
